Quick and dirty guide to our Web-SVN
====================================

- checkout our repository in SVN called "web/trunk".

- change/add stuff there 

- commit changes to SVN

-create interactive shell session (see http://apps.sourceforge.net/trac/sourceforge/wiki/Shell%20service):
 ssh -t USER,exult@shell.sourceforge.net create

- change dir to our webspace (cd /home/groups/e/ex/exult/htdocs)

- execute "./update.sh" (updates /home/../htdocs with SVN version and gives the right permissions to everyone)